*Multiscreen Interface~ `<home>~

All sorts of campaign information can be displayed here. To change to
a different screen, enter one of the following commands:

 `home~                             `help~
 `charinfo~ <id>                    `sceneinfo~ <id>
 `charlist~                         `scenelist~
 `addnpc~ <name> <hp>               `addpc~ <name> <realname> <hp>
 `setscene~ <id>                    `addscene~ <name>
 `give~ <id> <name>                 `remove~ <id> <item>
 `damage~ <int> <tar_id> <src_id>   `heal~ <int> <tar_id> <src_id> 
 `editchar~ <id> <column> <update>  `editscene~ <id> <column> <update>